Jerry’s Cherry Berries by Greener Mountain Boys  .  Vermont sungrown 😊.   Smells like berries and fuel smoke is super smooth .  She still needs a couple in cure but im loving this strain.
End of harvest is always bittersweet.  It’s so great to freely share with you all .
